              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23174483-eugene?shelf=2020">2020</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3167037814" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7417533511650764536">And with this, I’ve read most all of Mayle’s Provence books. As with his other non-fiction entries, this covers some of his adventures in French society and culture, gastronomy, and wine. None of the sequelae reached the heights of A Year In Provence, his first, but they’re all readable and entertaining. Subtitled Adventures With Knife, Fork, and Corkscrew, this entry concentrates on the gustatory pleasures to be found throughout France, and being a fellow who likes to eat and drink, I found it </span>
  <span id="freeText7417533511650764536" style="display:none">And with this, I’ve read most all of Mayle’s Provence books. As with his other non-fiction entries, this covers some of his adventures in French society and culture, gastronomy, and wine. None of the sequelae reached the heights of A Year In Provence, his first, but they’re all readable and entertaining. Subtitled Adventures With Knife, Fork, and Corkscrew, this entry concentrates on the gustatory pleasures to be found throughout France, and being a fellow who likes to eat and drink, I found it to be a pleasant last visit with the late Mr. Mayle. Bon Appetit!</span>
  <a data-text-id="7417533511650764536" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


